=\"top-news__en-title\">NEWS</span></h2>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"top-news__body\">\n            <ul class=\"top-news__list\">\n              <li class=\"top-news-item\">\n                <a href=\"/news/detail/20260601.html\" class=\"top-news-item__link\">\n                  <time class=\"top-news-item__time\">2026.06.01</time><span class=\"c-label -blue\">お知らせ</span>\n                  <p class=\"top-news-item__text\">プライバシーマークを更新しました。 </p>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"top-news-item\">\n                <a href=\"/news/detail/20260501.html\" class=\"top-news-item__link\">\n                  <time class=\"top-news-item__time\">2026.05.01</time><span class=\"c-label -blue\">お知らせ</span>\n                  <p class=\"top-news-item__text\">労働者派遣法に基づく情報提供について </p>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n            <a href=\"/news/\" class=\"top-news__list-link\">一覧はこちら</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <section class=\"top-section\">\n        <div class=\"top-section__inner\">\n          <h2 class=\"c-heading-main -large\">事業案内<span class=\"c-heading-main__subtext -blue\">WORKS</span></h2>\n\n          <section class=\"top-works\">\n            <h3 class=\"top-works__title\">クラウドシステム開発</h3>\n            <ul class=\"c-grid -wide\" style=\"justify-content: center;\">\n              <li data-aos=\"fade-up\" class=\"c-grid__col -col-3 -col-sp-6\">\n                <a href=\"/works/truck/\" class=\"top-works-link\">\n                  <div class=\"top-works-link__image\">\n                    <img src=\"/common/img/top/img_works_01.png\" srcset=\"/common/img/top/img_works_01@2x.png 2x\" alt=\"\">\n                  </div>\n                  <h4 class=\"top-works-link__title\">指示らくネット for トラック</h4>\n                  <p class=\"top-works-link__text\">Googleマップで作成したルートから運行指示書が作成できます！</p>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <li data-aos=\"fade-up\" c